<!doctype html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1" />
  <title>Career Board</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Manrope:wght@400;600;700&family=Space+Grotesk:wght@600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css" />
</head>
<body class="bg-cat-base text-cat-text min-h-screen flex flex-col font-sans selection:bg-cat-mauve selection:text-cat-base">
  
  <header class="sticky top-0 z-50 w-full border-b border-cat-surface1 bg-cat-base/80 backdrop-blur-md">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 h-16 flex items-center justify-between">
      <div class="text-2xl font-bold font-display tracking-tight text-cat-mauve">Career Board</div>
      <nav>
        <a class="px-4 py-2 text-sm font-bold text-cat-subtext0 hover:text-cat-text transition-colors" href="/login">ログイン</a>
        <a class="ml-2 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-bold bg-cat-mauve text-cat-base rounded-lg hover:bg-opacity-90 transition-all shadow-lg shadow-cat-mauve/20" href="/register">新規登録</a>
      </nav>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main class="flex-grow">
    <section class="container mx-auto px-4 py-20 md:py-32">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center space-y-8">
        <p class="inline-block px-3 py-1 text-xs font-bold tracking-wider text-cat-sky uppercase bg-cat-sky/10 rounded-full border border-cat-sky/20">
          キャリアの次の一歩へ
        </p>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-cat-text leading-tight">
          求人検索・応募・管理を<br/><span class="text-cat-mauve">一つのボードで。</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-cat-overlay2 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
          ユーザーはワンクリック応募、管理者は求人の作成・編集・削除。<br/>シンプルで直感的なダッシュボード体験を提供します。
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center pt-4">
          <a class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-3 text-base font-bold bg-cat-mauve text-cat-base rounded-xl hover:bg-opacity-90 transition-all shadow-xl shadow-cat-mauve/20 hover:-translate-y-1" href="/login">
            ログインして始める
          </a>
          <a class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-3 text-base font-bold text-cat-text bg-cat-surface0 border border-cat-surface1 rounded-xl hover:bg-cat-surface1 transition-all hover:-translate-y-1" href="#features">
            機能を見る
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="features" class="bg-cat-mantle py-20 border-t border-cat-surface0">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-cat-text mb-4">シンプルな機能構成</h2>
          <p class="text-cat-overlay1">必要な機能だけに絞った、使いやすいプラットフォーム</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
          <!-- Card 1 -->
          <div class="bg-cat-base p-8 rounded-2xl border border-cat-surface1 shadow-lg hover:border-cat-mauve/50 transition-colors group">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-cat-blue/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6 text-cat-blue group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M15 3h4a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v14a2 2 0 0 1-2 2h-4"/><polyline points="10 17 15 12 10 7"/><line x1="15" y1="12" x2="3" y2="12"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-cat-text mb-3">Login / Register</h3>
            <p class="text-cat-overlay2 leading-relaxed">
              メールとパスワードで簡単認証。セキュアな環境で、登録後はすぐにダッシュボードへアクセスできます。
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Card 2 -->
          <div class="bg-cat-base p-8 rounded-2xl border border-cat-surface1 shadow-lg hover:border-cat-mauve/50 transition-colors group">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-cat-green/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6 text-cat-green group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect width="7" height="9" x="3" y="3" rx="1"/><rect width="7" height="5" x="14" y="3" rx="1"/><rect width="7" height="9" x="14" y="12" rx="1"/><rect width="7" height="5" x="3" y="16" rx="1"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-cat-text mb-3">Dashboard</h3>
            <p class="text-cat-overlay2 leading-relaxed">
              求人一覧の閲覧、検索、応募までをワンストップで。応募済みの求人もマイページで管理可能。
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Card 3 -->
          <div class="bg-cat-base p-8 rounded-2xl border border-cat-surface1 shadow-lg hover:border-cat-mauve/50 transition-colors group">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-cat-red/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6 text-cat-red group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10"/><path d="m9 12 2 2 4-4"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-cat-text mb-3">Admin Control</h3>
            <p class="text-cat-overlay2 leading-relaxed">
              管理者権限で求人情報を自由に作成・編集・削除。直感的なインターフェースで管理が容易です。
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <footer class="bg-cat-base py-12 border-t border-cat-surface0">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 text-center text-cat-overlay0">
      <p>&copy; 2025 Career Board. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </footer>

</body>
</html>